  characterName: Oscar
  lines:
  - Our tests on the small robot went wonderfully! However.. there was a bit of an
    issue.
  - After successful tests we put it to work, but realised the robot was too small
    to complete anything meaningful! It just kept getting in the way.
  - Are you able to build us a couple larger ones? These will definitely help.
